e a good choice of career and the road to success in the creative industry.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">It is pretty interesting thing to be in charge and manage his own time and skill to respond at customer''s orders. I believe that it is a great experience, but until you have a decent network it is not a reliable situation.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">So I will recomend to start a freelance when you get the network or when you have time and don''t need a reliable situation (for your family for example).</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I believe that it can be a great experience to do few years in freelancing before to comeback on the traditional work, because it will bring you another point of view of work than you collegue, and it is always interesting to have differents experiences.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><strong>How succeed as a freelancer  in the creative industry?</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">I think in one word we can define how succeed : <strong>Professionalism</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">If you provide a good work as the customer expect and you are aware about your network you will be an happy and successfull creative freelancer !</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_313" align="aligncenter" width="580"]<img class="wp-image-313 size-full" src="http://vincent-berthet.net/en/project/blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/freelance2.jpg" alt="freelance2" width="580" height="349" /> Road to success[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Source :</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Statistics, from Campaign - <a href="http://www.campaignlive.co.uk/article/1346999/why-creative-industries-embracing-freelance-economy#" target="_blank">Why creative industries embracing freelance economy</a></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">General informations, from CreativeSkillset - <a href="http://vincent-berthet.net/en/blog/wor