(492, 1, '2017-02-13 14:38:00', '2017-02-13 14:38:00', '&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAs an other assessment for this module, I have also study more in details a subject in the creative industry in order to write a complete technical report around it.\n\nYou can find my <strong>Technical Report</strong> dealing about the<strong> Impact of social, casual and mobile game in the evolving games industry</strong> <a href="http://vincent-berthet.net/en/project/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/CA2_B00313298.pdf" target="_blank">right there</a>', 'Technical Report : Impact of social, casual and mobile games in the evolving games', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '489-autosave-v1', '', '', '2017-02-13 14:38:00', '2017-02-13 14:38:00', '', 489, 'http://vincent-berthet.net/en/project/blog/489-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
