oration: underline;"><span style="color: #993366; text-decoration: underline;">About the blog</span></span></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis blog has been designed to cover\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFeel free to add me on your social account !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-berthet" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-339 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-2-e1474996445897.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/vincentberthet42" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-338 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-1-e1474996410154.jpg" alt="face" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://twitter.com/_Sissouu" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-336 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-e1474996249174.jpg" alt="twitter" width="42" height="42" /></a>  <a href="http://www.instagram.com/heyklia/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-340 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-3-e1474996495265.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1zTh8-gfUpfaW8xvRnYHXw" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-341 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-4-e1474996521721.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 19:19:09', '2016-09-27 17:19:09', '', 264, 'http://127.0.