(345, 1, '2016-09-27 19:58:50', '2016-09-27 17:58:50', '<img class="size-full wp-image-319 aligncenter" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/mmm.jpg" alt="mmm" width="275" height="183" />\r\n\r\nHey, my name is Vincent, I am a 20 years old french student. I am currently studying Game Development in the University of the West of Scotland (UWS), and I wish you the welcome on my blog !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #993366; text-decoration: underline;">About me\r\n</span></span></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;"><img class="wp-image-320 alignleft" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/IMG_20160924_161106-2.jpg" alt="img_20160924_161106-2" width="504" height="283" /> For 8 years, computing and video games have taken an important part on my free time. First of all, I have started as a self-educated and I did many projects to discover deeper the computing field.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">That''s why, I decided to continue my studies in a first time in Electrical Engineering &amp; Industrial Computing during 2 years, in order to discover fields like automations, electronic, embeded computing which were fields that interested myself.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Finaly, I decided to forward in the computing. Instead of chose directly a french engineering school, I have prefered to take this year in a foreign country, in order to improve my english which is a very important skill in this field and also in the profesional world.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Moreover, I believe that this experience to discover an other culture, way of work, lifestyle, and also one of the interesting specifities of computing (Game Development) is a great opportunity\r\nfor me. Furthermore, I am sure about that this experience will help in my project of study after this year.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #993366; text-decoration: underline;">About the blog</span></span></h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThis blog has been designed to cover various topics associated with ethical and professional aspects of the creative industries, In a first time, I will deal with subjects submitted during the Creative Technology Profesionalism course and in the future  I would like to publish other topics close to this fields !\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nFeel free to add me on your social account !\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/in/vincent-berthet" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-339 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-2-e1474996445897.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://www.facebook.com/vincentberthet42" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-338 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-1-e1474996410154.jpg" alt="face" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://twitter.com/_Sissouu" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-336 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-e1474996249174.jpg" alt="twitter" width="42" height="42" /></a>  <a href="http://www.instagram.com/heyklia/" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-340 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-3-e1474996495265.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a> <a href="http://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1zTh8-gfUpfaW8xvRnYHXw" target="_blank"><img class="alignleft wp-image-341 size-full" src="http://127.0.0.1/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/03/free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix-4-e1474996521721.jpg" alt="free_flat_icons_13free_flat_icons_sensationalfix" width="42" height="42" /></a>', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-27 19:58:50', '2016-09-27 17:58:50', '', 264, 'http://127.0.0.1/blog/2016/09/27/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
